简介:   

长久以来，我一直怀疑人与人之间的相知，真正的相知，是遥不可及的。我很好奇于你是否会反对我的说法，虽然我仍觉得你会与我同心同感，与在很多其他事上一样...告诉我，是否有可能真正了解一个人？这是否值得我们去竭力追求？于我，唯有你的观点是可信的，是我乐于知晓的。For a long while now, I've suspected that connections with another person, real connection, simply isn't possible. I'm curious if you disagree, although I suspect you feel as I do in this, as you do in so many other things... So tell me is it possible to truly know another person? Is it even a worthwhile pursuing it? Yours is the only opinion I trust, the only point of view that holds even the faintest interest to me.


